===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
In oracle bone script {{Han compound|ls=ic|жңЁ|зӨә|t1=wood|t2=altar|nocap=y}} вҖ“ burning of wood to consult the gods. Originally the same character as {{zh-l|*еҘҲ}}

In the modern form {{zh-l|*жңЁ}} has corrupted into {{zh-l|*еҮә}}, thus the character can be interpreted as {{Han compound|еҮә|зӨә|c1=p|c2=s|t2=altar|ls=psc|nocap=y}}.

